skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gift whispers
des:
Start your day with a whisper cookie from the heavenly gift giver through his gift whisperer, Michael Mathews. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next whisper cookie. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
